Package com.jcabi.odesk Description

Object Oriented Odesk API.

The only dependency you need is (check our latest version available at odesk.jcabi.com): 

<depedency>
   <groupId>com.jcabi</groupId>
   <artifactId>jcabi-odesk</artifactId>
 </dependency>
